<http://status.aws.amazon.com/|Informational message: Increased Async API Latencies>
We are investigating increased Async API latencies in the EU-WEST-1 Region.

<http://status.aws.amazon.com/|Informational message: Increased Async API Latencies>
We have identified the root cause of increased Async API latencies in the EU-WEST-1 Region and continue to work toward resolution.

<http://status.aws.amazon.com/|Service is operating normally: [RESOLVED] Increased Async API Latencies>
Between 6:59 AM and 8:56 AM PDT we experienced increased latencies for the Lambda Async API in the EU-WEST-1 Region. The issue has been resolved and the service is operating normally.
